{"tid":11491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] LIHKG應唔應該有emoji?","createTime":"2016-11-29T10:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T11:47:43.000Z","uid":16491,"like":8,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad3977307be0ffbf915f9d3dfde8d2ac476369f7","tid":11491,"uid":16491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:03:24.000Z","msg":"有：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講多幾句，我當初其中一個鐘意高登嘅理由就係因為高登icon。高登嘅icon傳神又盞鬼，每款都表達唔同意思或情感，不知幾正。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我平日Whatsapp，以至用手機同人傾計，從來唔用emoji，因為emoji唔好睇（個人認為），加上實在俾人用到太濫，完全無傳意嘅作用。一個😂，根本咩都表達唔到，而久而久之，見到就有一種厭惡感。至於其實emojis，都唔覺有意思。<br />\n<br />\n但上高登，一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，勝過千言萬語。<br />\n<br />\n我平日生活已經忍受排山倒海且空洞嘅emoji，上LIHKG，我實在唔想又要係腦海開emoji filter，會攰。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得有高登icon，夠晒啦。"},{"pid":"8c802a00e104f8408e183992601853892bdf3c66","tid":11491,"uid":29326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:06:31.000Z","msg":"唔係太多濫用我覺得有都冇所謂<br />\n姐係唔好係咁😂😂😂😂個d就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92510de17792317e1a85958fd57b05304453d991","tid":11491,"uid":2984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"講乜都假<br />\n班emoji撚唔肯接受佢地只係少數既事實"},{"pid":"4604a4cc34ea473fe18f02f4bdd35cfc8ee6f9d5","tid":11491,"uid":10487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:28:49.000Z","msg":"之前覺得唔應該有.. 但見到有個post 類似key 過三關.. 好有創意 轉左態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cad2e020ab53d7aa72989a75b3c857b233e247e","tid":11491,"uid":10487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:29:32.000Z","msg":"🚕🐎🐘💩👑💩🐘🐎🚕<br />\n⬜️⬜️⬜️⬜️⬜️⬜️⬜️⬜️⬜️<br />\n⬜️🔫⬜️⬜